nodes.text: A clone who served as a shock trooper sergeant with the Coruscant Guard accompanied Commander Stone and several other troopers of the Diplomatic Escort Group with Senator Kharrus and Representative Jar Jar Binks to Florrum.

He survived the crash of their shuttle after which he helped Representative Binks bury Senator Kharrus and informed him of the acid geysers. He, along with the other clones, survived the mission and departed Florrum aboard the Twilight.
